00:37:22.322 --> 00:37:25.239
<i>v imenu resnice in logike

00:37:25.534 --> 00:37:29.402
<i>z veseljem izjavljam,
da bomo podpisali sporazum.

00:37:29.663 --> 00:37:32.153
Podpisuje sporazum!

