–Bi rad videl pravi Panamski prekop?

00:37:59.945 --> 00:38:04.025
Stokrat sem videl
ta mini prekop.

00:38:04.324 --> 00:38:07.028
To praviš,
ker imaš samo čoln z jadrom.

00:38:07.286 --> 00:38:10.951
Čoln?
Titanik imam!

00:38:11.791 --> 00:38:13.949
Potem pa ga potopi.

00:38:14.251 --> 00:38:18.083
Vsa Panama praznuje na ulici,
ti pa nisi nič vesela?

00:38:18.463 --> 00:38:21.713
Vesela česa?
–Česa?

00:38:22.675 --> 00:38:27.172
Očitno te nikoli niso ujeli
klinčevi marinci. –Prosim?

00:38:27.889 --> 00:38:29.762
Bogataško dekle.

00:38:30.059 --> 00:38:32.728
Pusti me.
–Boš zdaj jezna?

00:38:32.978 --> 00:38:34.969
Ja, traparije govoriš.

00:38:36.856 --> 00:38:40.521
Ponujajo, da nam bodo vrnili
naše ozemlje leta 1999.

00:38:40.735 --> 00:38:42.811
Čez 20 let!

00:38:43.280 --> 00:38:46.067
Hudiča, to je naše!

00:38:46.490 --> 00:38:50.655
